column16: Josh Donaldson doubles (6) on a line drive to center fielder Jarrod Dyson.  Kevin Pillar out at home on the throw, center fielder Jarrod Dyson to shortstop Taylor Motter to catcher Mike Zunino.

Ryan Goins grounds out, shortstop Taylor Motter to first baseman Danny Valencia.
